tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review:
I work in an entertainment industry and my smile has value. I had done some amateur adjustments more then a decade ago in a small town, to my frontal teeth n now was the time to repair for good. I Thank Dr. Sejal from bottom of my heart for completing my childhood dream of a lovely, Symmetrical smile Today. " I can't stop Smiling now".
She was the only one, who could understand what I ment when I wanted to do this procedure and how I wanted it to look like ( Compare to 4 other experts I consulted before her) Value for the Money and My time. Thanks a ton üôèüèΩ God Bless
Overall experience was very good..The way we were treated was good... Treatment was very quick..Xray was taken immediately and extraction was done very well...

Doctor is punctual, friendly and equiped with all the latest equipments. All the appointments took place without any delay. All problems were explained in detailed and then provided necessary and correct treatment. There was immediate relief from toothache and in case RCT- it was painless. Highly recommended for All dental issues. I would surely visit regularly for follow ups.
